<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Mussa - Portfolio</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }
        
        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }
        
        header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6a11cb 0%, #2575fc 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 80px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .profile-img {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            object-fit: cover;
            border: 5px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .tagline {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: white;
            color: #2575fc;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        section {
            padding: 80px 0;
        }
        
        h2 {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }
        
        .about-content {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 40px;
        }
        
        .about-text {
            flex: 1;
        }
        
        .skills {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        
        .skill {
            background: #e9ecef;
            padding: 8px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        
        .projects-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
        }
        
        .project-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .project-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
        }
        
        .project-img {
            height: 200px;
            background: #6a11cb;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .project-content {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .project-content h3 {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }
        
        .contact-info {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        .contact-item {
            margin: 15px 0;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        
        footer {
            background: #2c3e50;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 0;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .about-content {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            
            h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            
            section {
                padding: 60px 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <!-- REPLACE THIS WITH YOUR PICTURE -->
            <!-- Option 1: Use your GitHub profile picture -->
            <img src="https://github.com/mussa321.png" alt="Mussa" class="profile-img">
            
            <!-- Option 2: If you upload a picture to your repository, use this instead -->
            <!-- <img src="profile.jpg" alt="Mussa" class="profile-img"> -->
            
            <h1>Mussa</h1>
            <p class="tagline">Full-Stack Developer & Problem Solver</p>
            <a href="#projects" class="btn">View My Work</a>
        </div>
    </header>
    
    <section id="about">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>About Me</h2>
            <div class="about-content">
                <div class="about-text">
                    <p>I'm a passionate developer from Ruvuma, Tanzania with a love for creating efficient, user-friendly web applications. I enjoy turning complex problems into simple, beautiful solutions.</p>
                    <p>When I'm not coding, you can find me exploring new technologies, contributing to open source projects, or learning something new.</p>
                    
                    <h3 style="margin-top: 30px;">Skills</h3>
                    <div class="skills">
                        <span class="skill">JavaScript</span>
                        <span class="skill">HTML/CSS</span>
                        <span class="skill">React</span>
                        <span class="skill">Node.js</span>
                        <span class="skill">Python</span>
                        <span class="skill">Git</span>
                        <span class="skill">Responsive Design</span>
                        <span class="skill">UI/UX</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <section id="projects" style="background: #f1f3f5;">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>My Projects</h2>
            <div class="projects-grid">
                <div class="project-card">
                    <div class="project-img">Project 1</div>
                    <div class="project-content">
                        <h3>E-Commerce Website</h3>
                        <p>A fully responsive e-commerce platform with product filtering, cart functionality, and secure checkout process.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="project-card">
                    <div class="project-img">Project 2</div>
                    <div class="project-content">
                        <h3>Task Management App</h3>
                        <p>A productivity application for managing tasks with drag-and-drop functionality and team collaboration features.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="project-card">
                    <div class="project-img">Project 3</div>
                    <div class="project-content">
                        <h3>Weather Dashboard</h3>
                        <p>A clean, intuitive weather application that displays current conditions and forecasts for multiple locations.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <section id="contact">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>
            <div class="contact-info">
                <p>I'm always interested in new opportunities and collaborations.</p>
                
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <strong>Email:</strong> mussandauka321@gmail.com
                </div>
                
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <strong>Location:</strong> Ruvuma, Tanzania
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <p>&copy; 2024 Mussa. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 10px; opacity: 0.8;">Built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
